<lyrics>[V1]
 1- hlạ ạ̉tyt lqlby ạlrqyq ạ̉wtnsẖlny mn khfy ạlsḥyq?
 tsyl ạ̉dmʿy wtbky lkrby ạ̉tḥn ʿly wtnzʿ ḍyqy
 wsṭ ạnhyạry ykẖbw ạlrjạʾ ykẖtnq wsṭ ẓlạmy ạlḍyạʾ
 yjwl ybḥtẖ lyjd mnfdẖ wyrkḍ wyʿdw wlys mn ʿzạʾ
 ạlqrạr - fstry fy qlbk wạ̉mạny fy drbk
 yạ qwty wṣkẖrty ậty ạ̹ly̱ ḥbk
 2- ạ̉ty bḥzny wạ̉bgẖy ạlʿnạq fmn swạk ybdl ạlạ̹kẖfạq
 fạ̉nt tkẖrj mn mry ḥlwaⁿạ wmrậk rby ạ̉ʿẓm tryạq
 nfsy ạlrạjyẗ tạ̉ty bạnksạr tstgẖytẖ bk mn wyl ạlmrạr
 hl tʿynhạ wtnṣt lhạ hl tṭlqhạ wtḥṭm ạljdạr?
 3- wṭny ʿndk wạlạ̉rḍ mryrẗ ạ̉nạ hnạ wạ̉bgẖạk fyạllḥyrẗ
 lys ly ạ̉mtʿẗ wlạ dẖhb wạ̉ftdy ạlwqt fạlạ̉yạm sẖryrẗ
 fltạ̉ty yạ rjạỷy bqwtk fḥyạty lạ sẖyʾ dwn mḥbtk
 wqlby ạltạỷb yṣrkẖ ạ̹lyk ytrjy̱ ʿṭfk wystʿṭf rḥmtk</lyrics>
